; Coverage test for post.cc line 165
; Test that transactions without a code return empty for the code field.
; Also tests get_code returning NULL_VALUE when no code is present.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 (123) Payment
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(code)|\n'
|
|
123|
123|
end test
